message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product to you for $95. I think it's a great deal for something of this quality.
Thank you for your offer, Alice. I appreciate your suggestion. I am willing to pay $88 for the product.
Thanks for your offer, Bob. I understand you're looking for a good deal. How about we meet in the middle at $92?
I appreciate your willingness to negotiate, Alice. I would like to counter with an offer of $89 for the product.
